author: Justin Block
title: Former Louisville Cardinals Basketball Players Acknowledge Stripper Parties
text:
Former Louisville Cardinals Basketball Players Acknowledge Stripper Parties ESPN By John Barr and Jeff Goodman Posted: 10/20/2015 09:29 AM EDT Joe Robbins via Getty Images 
LOUISVILLE, Ky. -- Five former University of Louisville basketball players and recruits told Outside the Lines that they attended parties at a campus dorm from 2010 to 2014 that included strippers paid for by the team's former graduate assistant coach, Andre McGee.
